---
title: Mediterranean Chickpea & Veggie Stew with Parmesan & Garlic Panini
description: If you're planning to stay in with a cosy homecooked dinner, then this stew fits the criteria. Tomato and chickpeas come
together in a snap to create the base for the roast veggies to soak in. Dig in and enjoy the comfort of an easy to make
and tasty dinner.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
